<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Students entering with AP credit, credit from other advanced placement programs or examinations, and/or joint enrollment credit may take the Regents' Tests during their first two semesters of enrollment. They are not subject to System- mandated course requirements unless they have earned at least forty five (45) hours and been enrolled at least two semesters.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.atlm.edu" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
